    Message(MessageError),
    UnsupportedOutputKind(u8),

    MigratedFundsAmountOverflow(u128),

    ConsumedTreasuryOutputMismatch(MilestoneId, MilestoneId),
    NegativeBalance(i64),
    BalanceOverflow(i128),
    InvalidBalance(u64),
    BalanceDiffOverflow(i128),
    InvalidBalanceDiff(i64),
    PackableOption,
}
